hopobject.body: Who's calling? tamoxifen citrate bodybuilding With her Southern graciousness, Mrs. Boggs was said to charm, flatter and persuade even the most curmudgeonly of her male counterparts in Congress. As a representative for nine terms, she used those skills to support civil rights — eventually becoming the only white member of Congress elected from a majority-black district — and to promote legislation that helped women and children.
